{"tid":348831,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"who cares if one more light goes out?","createTime":"2017-08-06T05:18:34.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-07T18:22:56.000Z","uid":29540,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"df15c6f7ace4ad6c3d9d365e71c9cdcb794e6c72","tid":348831,"uid":29540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T05:18:34.000Z","msg":"in a sky of a million stars"},{"pid":"f8d89c2915032520636fcf78009e847dca43110d","tid":348831,"uid":29540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T05:20:11.000Z","msg":"We saw brilliance, when the world, was asleep<br />\n明曦揮灑，當世界萬物，正在沉睡<br />\n<br />\nThere are things that we can have, but can't keep<br />\n有些事物我們曾經擁有，卻不會長留"},{"pid":"a2324e621047857626715477fe95a7c90d380bfb","tid":348831,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T05:20:56.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">得到一刻開心過後 不開心<br />\n怎麼都不開心 誰責任<br />\n拖拖拉拉最後還是 不發奮<br />\n永遠看不見未來 被愛軟禁<br />\n<br />\n矛盾只因深愛著 你知嗎<br />\n誰期望這刻擁抱完 然後吵架<br />\n你為我放一場煙花 跌下來瘡疤<br />\n痛定思痛 未來 算吧<br />\n回頭看最初多快樂 記得嗎<br />\n竟會沒決心成家<br />\n當你遲遲未改變 就讓我改變吧<br />\n這個決定多可怕<br />\n<br />\n偏偏分手這種對白 說出口<br />\n永遠有個傷口 移不走<br />\n搞不清楚我累還是 你不夠<br />\n作個最適當決定 別再佔有<br />\n<br />\n矛盾只因深愛著 你知嗎<br />\n誰期望這刻擁抱完 然後吵架<br />\n你為我放一場煙花 跌下來瘡疤<br />\n痛定思痛 未來 算吧<br />\n回頭看最初多快樂 記得嗎<br />\n竟會沒決心成家<br />\n當你遲遲未改變 就讓我改變吧<br />\n這個決定多可怕<br />\n<br />\n落魄的淚如雨下 別軟化<br />\n天會同情我嗎 只好逼我瀟灑 明白嗎<br />\n<br />\n矛盾只因深愛著 你知嗎<br />\n誰尋覓愛的一個人 然後不嫁<br />\n仰望過那一襲婚紗 美麗而孤寡<br />\n你沒想過 未來 對吧<br />\n回頭看最初多快樂 你捨得嗎<br />\n竟會沒決心成家<br />\n當你仍然未開竅 就讓我開竅吧<br />\n我替你自私好嗎</span></span>"},{"pid":"419c2622aad7bf23f014d5925acd11829ecef074","tid":348831,"uid":29540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T05:23:00.000Z","msg":"The reminders, pull the floor from your feet<br />\n那些往事的提醒，把你從現實抽離<br />\n<br />\nIn the kitchen, one more chair than you need, oh<br />\n廚房裡，多出了一張空椅子<br />\n<br />\nAnd you're angry, and you should be, it's not fair<br />\n你的怒火湧上心頭，這是能理解的，無解是上天對你的不公平<br />\n<br />\nJust 'cause you can't see it, doesn't mean it, isn't there<br />\n然而看不見之物，不代表，它並不存在"},{"pid":"357dade712d76ba5cd196af104638efeb8276748","tid":348831,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T05:26:45.000Z","msg":"Do i exist for you?<br />\n難道我存在是為了你"},{"pid":"2c1d7836fb84dcbcc32a90844d2088ea6c1e91c1","tid":348831,"uid":29540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T05:29:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Do i exist for you?<br />\n難道我存在是為了你</blockquote><br />\n驚D垃圾仔唔識英文"},{"pid":"1b34de415a13209ba430dc86fca4ea83ce1c500f","tid":348831,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T05:31:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>Do i exist for you?<br />\n難道我存在是為了你</blockquote><br />\n驚D垃圾仔唔識英文</blockquote><br />\n愛你"},{"pid":"67b4549acd66a2748fe44d226b08a3b389e185d7","tid":348831,"uid":29540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T05:32:26.000Z","msg":"Who cares if one more light goes out?<br />\n誰人會在意一顆星的消逝？<br />\n<br />\nIn a sky of a million stars<br />\n在繁星滿佈的夜空<br />\n<br />\nIt flickers, flickers<br />\n那星頑強地，閃耀<br />\n<br />\nWho cares when someone's time runs out?<br />\n誰人會在意陌生人的生命終結？"},{"pid":"98611fd169222a8334f237d42fe56301b959ce63","tid":348831,"uid":828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T05:36:14.000Z","msg":"I care<br />\n健康促進服務雲"},{"pid":"10ec41b4e5cc1487c4f279e13328296d137e21f2","tid":348831,"uid":29540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T06:26:24.000Z","msg":"I don&rsquo;t like my mind right now<br />\nStacking up problems that are so unnecessary<br />\nWish that I could slow things down<br />\nI wanna let go but there&rsquo;s comfort in the panic"},{"pid":"f9b5252190b08a99431b54d890a8a1c26f9aff9f","tid":348831,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyT